{"tid":574212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身高180說英國腔　全球首個男性性愛機械人將上市","createTime":"2018-02-27T07:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T10:45:28.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"71430014fbca55bff5d7dca709263a6e0839f601","tid":574212,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"正當「性愛娃娃妓院」(Sex Doll Brothel)在歐陸多國走紅之際，一家專門生產這類高擬真情趣娃娃的公司日前宣布，全球第一尊男性的擬真性愛機器人「亨利」(Henry)，研發工作已經進入最後階段，很快就會問世。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180227/640_5c6df58db29d5eb456264aedfee7b5cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180227%2F640_5c6df58db29d5eb456264aedfee7b5cc.jpg&h=a9d44479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他叫做「亨利」(Henry)，身高180公分，體重輕了些，只有約38公斤(英制6 stone)，小麥色的肌膚，有著勻稱的6塊腹肌，能說一口標準的英國腔英語。製作研發的Realbotix公司估計，只要8千英鎊(約台幣32.8萬元)就能把基本款的亨利帶回家，但<span style=\"color: red;\">「亨利」的生殖器官可以接受買家訂作，形狀長短大小都可以指定，價錢自然也會高些</span>，但也不會超過1.1萬英鎊(約台幣45.1萬元)。<br />\n<br />\nRealbotix公司的負責人麥穆倫(Matt McMullen)表示：「女人和男人一樣，也會感到寂寞」，「雖然大家稱這個為性愛娃娃，其實它們主要的功能，在於『陪伴』，在這個電腦世界裡，人類正在失去人與人間的互動」。亨利雖然是機械人，但有表情、會眨眼，透過智慧手機app，可以簡單操作，他會說一口道地的英國腔英語，內建了許多浪漫的情詩、歌詞與對話，是個「浪漫高手」。<br />\n<br />\n目前研發進入最後階段，麥穆倫不諱言，最困難的就是，要如何在「實戰」時，讓亨利能像真的男人一般「行動」，畢竟以目前知道的「規格」看來，亨利身上大部分的地方，沒有安裝機械裝置，是不會自己行動的。<br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學歐尼爾博士(Dr. Cathy O'Neil)表示，她相信，「亨利可以幫助寂寞的女性」，「妳怎麼能不愛這個雄赳赳的機械男人呢？更何況他們的『表現』很可能比真男人更好」。而在Realbotix的官方《IG》頁面上，則有網友留言：「希望他身上能有個『緊急停止』按鈕，天知道呢？妳可能會被他做到死」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"e5363a6c8c99a19d9b5add0ed788dc10aacab54f","tid":574212,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"電動洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf3e1024c77d65e197db3522d29271eccddf1a8","tid":574212,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"電動陽具 插耳鼻喉"},{"pid":"a09beac8a5049b30ca1cb87f9fc4ad9d833fd88a","tid":574212,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"82a5e7347a3c80d524cc923d921d8af5dfa058d8","tid":574212,"uid":29090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2010/time_100/t100art_robert_pattinson.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.timeinc.net%2Ftime%2Fphotoessays%2F2010%2Ftime_100%2Ft100art_robert_pattinson.jpg&h=a89dcc3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d6668f8aaad621c38b4111ee421a174532fccd7","tid":574212,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"抄我樣。。。"},{"pid":"01e951fb9418abac7dc46b7dc3114053bbbfe303","tid":574212,"uid":36010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"識唔識變身同噴汁？"},{"pid":"16c270e2c73f1bf3741b4574aa1ae9d69a06f4a2","tid":574212,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"可唔可以梳一梳下個頭先呀??"},{"pid":"a799765810d116e7d4a12388593261887add8c19","tid":574212,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會GAY佬買比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1550a895def903a01055277406d8f4e4896ef6","tid":574212,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"物化男性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75270c2c130ba3f83499ffac0831b3856d55419e","tid":574212,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a799765810d116e7d4a12388593261887add8c19","tid":574212,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會GAY佬買比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"你岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"h